overview.en: Go is an expandable, high-performance, low-cost, decentralized encrypted currency and block chain based on ETF intelligent contract. It supports intelligent contract and distributed application. Go's mission is to provide a scalable, low-cost, energy-efficient platform for digital currency and distributed application.
overview.zh: Go是基于以太坊的智能合约，是一款可扩展，高性能，低成本，分散式的加密货币和区块链，支持智能合约和分布式应用程序，Go的使命是为数字货币和分散式应用提供可扩展，低成本，高能效的平台。
